sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Refresh Trigger
    participant RefreshW as RefreshUpstreamSourceWorkflow
    participant MSM as MSM API
    participant SS as SimpleStream Source

    T->>RefreshW: start workflow (boot_source_id, msm_url, msm_jwt)
    
    RefreshW->>+MSM: GET boot source config<br/>(GET_BOOT_SOURCE_ACTIVITY)
    note over MSM: retrieve source config<br/>index_url, keyring<br/>(selections not used in refresh)
    MSM-->>-RefreshW: GetBootSourceResult<br/>(index_url, keyring)
    
    RefreshW->>+SS: Fetch SimpleStream index<br/>(FETCH_SS_INDEXES)
    note over SS: download index file<br/>verify signature if .sjson<br/>extract product URLs
    SS-->>-RefreshW: FetchSsIndexesResult<br/>(products[] URLs)
    
    loop for each product index URL
        RefreshW->>+SS: Fetch asset list<br/>(FETCH_SS_ASSETS_ACTIVITY)
        note over SS: download product index<br/>verify signature if needed<br/>extract available OS assets<br/>(exclude bootloader assets)
        SS-->>-RefreshW: FetchAssetListResult<br/>(assets[] AvailableAsset)
    end
    
    RefreshW->>+MSM: PUT available assets<br/>(PUT_AVAILABLE_ASSETS_ACTIVITY)
    note over MSM: update catalog of available assets<br/>(metadata only, no downloads)<br/>used for selection UI
    MSM-->>-RefreshW: done
    
    RefreshW-->>T: done (returns True)

